headline: AppLovin: High Volatility Into Earnings, Margins In Focus, A Deserved Valuation
summary: APP's Q3 GAAP EPS of $1.25 beat expectations, with revenue up 39% YoY; the stock surged 46% post-earnings. Explore more details here.
